  name: "Foteini Karamitsou",
  image: foteiniImg,
  bio: `Foteini is a special education student, passionate about youth work and storytelling. Curious about cultures, she shares Erasmus+ stories through blogging and social media.`,
  bio_el: `Η Φωτεινή είναι φοιτήτρια Ειδικής Αγωγής, παθιασμένη με τη νεανική εργασία και την αφήγηση. Περιεργάζεται τους πολιτισμούς και μοιράζεται ιστορίες Erasmus+ μέσω blogging και social media.`
}, {
  name: "Sotiris Kouroukafopoulos",
  image: sotirisImg,
  bio: `Sotirios is a 21-year-old Law student from Greece, active in Erasmus+ and volunteering. He's a youth leader with strong teamwork skills and a passion for intercultural learning.`,
